name.value: SAP SuccessFactors Recruiting Management to People Answers Assessment

query.value: SELECT address, applicationLocale, cellPhone, city, contactEmail, country, firstName, gender, homePhone, lastName, middleName, state, zip FROM JobApplication$${header.applicationTemplateId} WHERE id = '${xpath.//queryAssessmentOrderResponse/AssessmentOrder/applicationId}'
SELECT hiringManagerUserName FROM JobRequisition$${header.jobReqTemplateId} WHERE id = '${xpath.//queryAssessmentOrderResponse/AssessmentOrder/jobReqId}'
SELECT email FROM User WHERE username = '${xpath.//queryJobRequisitionResponse/JobRequisition/hiringManagerUserName}'

SELECT applicationId, applicationTemplateId, assessmentPackageCode, candidateId, candidateTemplateId, clientId, handbackUrl, id, jobReqId, jobReqTemplateId, partnerId, vendorCode FROM AssessmentOrder WHERE id = '${header.assessmentOrderId}'

wrapContent.value:
<ns1:rcmAssessmentResponse xmlns:ns1="com.successfactors.alert">
   <ns1:entityId>${property.entityId}</ns1:entityId>
   <ns1:status>99</ns1:status>
   <ns1:statusDate>${date:now:yyyyMMddHHmmss}</ns1:statusDate>
   <ns1:statusDetails></ns1:statusDetails>
   <ns1:errorCode>Invalid EntityName Error</ns1:errorCode>
   <ns1:errorMessage>Expected entityName AssessmentOrder. Received entityName ${property.entityName}</ns1:errorMessage>
</ns1:rcmAssessmentResponse>
